I took part in a photo contest with TropicalTraveller and I am very delighted that two of my photos made it to the top 10! The colourful structure and the cocktail drink were two of my submissions. The categories were: Pitons, Scenic, Sea, Sunset, Food/drink, Flora, Waterfall, People and Structures. I made it in two categories, food/drink and structures. Woohoo!
The top three winners were chosen. Congratulations to the winners! Their submissions were awesome! It must have been tough choosing winners!! It was fun:) I look forward to another contest!

The Miss Fashion Week Jersey City finale event will be held in September 22, 2017. This will not be your typical finale event; we are merging pageantry, high fashion, models and musicians together to bring a fresh vibe for fashion productions!

The total of 15 runner ups will come out to compete against the models in their category. The competing categories are; Runway, Swimwear, All White and High Fashion.

We are expecting agreat turn out of over 200 guest and vendors! Come out enjoy the show, great fashion and vibes!
